This paper is primarily focused on wireless networking and communication, which falls under the category of computer science - networking and internet architecture (cs.NI). The paper also heavily relies on deep learning techniques, which suggests that it could also be categorized under machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper discusses the design of a hardware/software architecture, which could fall under the category of systems and control (cs.SY). The paper also mentions the use of coding rate, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT). Finally, the paper discusses the use of modulation and OFDM parameter recognition, which could fall under the category of computer science - architecture (cs.AR).
